andalous, hedonistic side to the blue-blooded scion.%0a%3c %0a%3c '''Black Market:''' Though he's less active than he used to be, Anthony keeps his ear to the ground when it comes to the underground network of stolen goods, especially the sorts of high-ticket items he specializes in, or the unusual sort the Order desires.  Sometimes that information means dealing with unsavory types.%0a%3c [[%3c%3c]]%0a%3c %25%25http://wantonwicked.gamingsandbox.com/wiki/images/wod/headers/wodm_con.png%0a%3c %0a%3c [[%3c%3c]]%0a%3c %25%25http://wantonwicked.gamingsandbox.com/wiki/images/wod/headers/wodm_q.png%0a%3c ''"Where your treasure is, there will your heart be also."'' - [[Some Guy]]%0a%3c %0a%3c [[%3c%3c]]%0a%3c %0a%3c (:include CityBook.MortalNavigationBar:)%0a\ No newline at end of file%0a
